OL,5, Three major non-governmental           
OL,6, organisations (NGOs) have halted work  
OL,7, in Afghanistan after women were banned 
OL,8, from working for them by the Taliban.  
OL,10,FIn a joint statement, Care             
OL,11,FInternational, the Norwegian Refugee   
OL,12,FCouncil (NRC) and Save the Children    
OL,13,Fsaid they would be unable to continue  
OL,14,Ftheir work "without our female staff". 
OL,16,FThe aid groups are "demanding" that    
OL,17,Fwomen can continue to work for them.   
OL,19,FAfghanistan's ruling Taliban have been 
OL,20,Fsteadily repressing women's rights.    
